{"tid":1815762,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"Facebook不停打壓真相 有乜解救？","createTime":"2020-01-07T18:23:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-08T00:55:05.000Z","uid":145118,"like":19,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"5a7b2f90542ce2c21b933b10120c65219dfd1cf9","tid":1815762,"uid":145118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T18:23:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xsHpn2j.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxsHpn2j.png&h=b0a4f2e6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">我連續開三個帳都被禁晒言！</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">FB奶共 奶到痴撚線</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">想問有無得攻擊返FB?</span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">可以考慮減少睇fb廣告或落廣告，對吧？</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n煩死，一個星期封一次，不過我有好多帳仲未用完，可以再開，反正唔洗本，但問題一出po(關於反送中)基本上好快被禁言。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e56d15ca5d4fc8c89af5e108e1add730f5718bff","tid":1815762,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T18:29:33.000Z","msg":"唔用fb<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f47cd4d1991a7fca38fc09e92d251f50513cdc28","tid":1815762,"uid":53524,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"e56d15ca5d4fc8c89af5e108e1add730f5718bff","tid":1815762,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T18:29:33.000Z","msg":"唔用fb<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T18:31:34.000Z","msg":"問題係好多人用緊<